Package: genhaz
Title: General Hazard Models for Survival Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    c(person("Aaron", "Jehle", email = "aaron.jehle@mail.de", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Mark", "Clements", email = "mark.clements@ki.se", role = c("aut")))
Description: Fits penalized cubic spline generalized hazards (GH) models
    for survival data, encompassing proportional hazards (PH), accelerated failure
    time (AFT), additive hazards (AH), and the full GH specification. Smoothing parameter selection via a modified leave-one-out cross-validation (LCV)
    criterion. Also provides mixture Weibull utilities for data generation and
    simulation studies.
